title: Welcome to TayApp
message: We are happy to see you here. Please note that the app is still in its early stages. This means, for example, that data on Swift's discography might be incomplete or sometimes incorrect. I am working on it though! (So much data, so little timeâ€¦) ,:) Feel free to look around a bit. If you have any questions, comments or other concerns visit us on Discord. Have fun! :)
